videos.description: Jimmy Whitt Jr. steps in front of an errant Edric Dennis pass, then goes the other way for the Arkansas dunk.

videos.description: Kevin Samuel sends Reggie Chaney's dunk attempt away, then later in the possession Chaney misses an uncontested dunk.
